        "content": "\n**Current state: zero tests.** No test files exist anywhere in the repo, and `requirements.txt` doesn't even include `pytest`. This is a from-scratch analysis of 1,505 lines across 8 modules.\n\nRecommended dev dependencies before starting: `pytest`, `pytest-asyncio`, `respx` (or `httpx.MockTransport`) for mocking `httpx`, `freezegun` (or `unittest.mock.patch` on `datetime`) for time-sensitive tests.\n\n---\n\n",
